snippet.title: Theme song
snippet.description:
/!\ Reupload 

We just received the sfx and demo's soundtracks a few days ago so to celebrate it, we're showing you the game's main theme with of course the title screen to grasp the atmosphere properly! (You already saw it, but it's better with music!)

Also, we would like to thank you all for your shares and comments! It motivates us a lot and even if we have less game related content to show you, please know that we're working very hard on it! We just can't show you everything (and we are in the middle of administrative tasks orz).

We're hoping that you will like the main theme! We're loving it! Do not hesitate to tell us what you're thinking of it, and go check the compositor's channel!

Compositor : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC5KuXXBW8rXX06LVxFCkzeg
